%% Evidence: LM-E001, LM-E002, LM-E003, LM-E004, LM-E005, LM-E006, LM-E007
sequenceDiagram
  participant Host
  participant Page as /listings/create
  participant Form as CreateListingForm
  participant Upload as /api/upload
  participant API as POST /api/listings
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant Search as Search projections

  Host->>Page: Open create page
  Page->>Form: Render authenticated form
  Host->>Form: Enter details and add images
  Form->>Upload: Upload listing images
  Upload-->>Form: Return uploaded URLs or errors
  Host->>Form: Publish
  Form->>API: POST JSON with X-Idempotency-Key
  API->>API: Validate CSRF, auth, profile, schema, language, geocode, images
  API->>DB: Transaction with advisory lock, collision checks, listing/location write
  API->>Search: Mark dirty and run post-create side effects
  API-->>Form: 201 { id } or validation/collision error
  Form-->>Host: Clear draft and redirect on success
